Sheila: I still haven't sold my ticket...
    -> Player: I think you should enter the Omen City contest after all.
        <<set $Sheila_Affection += 1>>
        <<set $Sheila_Activated = 1>>
        Sheila: Really? 
        Sheila: You're right! We can do this! T
        Sheila: Thanks {$playerName}.
