title: chapter2_SSSpam_StopItMilitia_Attack
tags:
---
Intercom: Ladies and Gentlemen, this is an official announcement. 
Intercom: I hope you are enjoying your journey with your Familiar slaves. 
Intercom: I regret to inform you that the StopIt! Militia have taken control of this vessel and will be seizing your Familiars shortly. 
Intercom: Please, stay calm and do not resist, else there will be serious consequences.
Intercom: Goodbye.
