title: chapter2_SSSpam_StopItMilitia_Matthias_PlayerWins
tags:
---
Matthias: I knew you could do it, {$playerName}! 
Regiment Leader: Damn it! 
Regiment Leader: Quick, let's get out of here!
Captain Drake: That was close. 
Captain Drake: My Lichen would be gone right now if it wasn't for you both.
Matthias: It sounds like things have quietened down out there. 
Matthias: Please wait here while I go and take a look.
Matthias: The StopIt! Militia have fled! 
Matthias: It turns out they met with much more resistance than expected. 
Matthias: Unfortunately, they did manage to take some of the ship's Familiar crew with them but your defeat of their leader spooked them so much that they abandoned the rest of their scheme. 
    -> Player: I'm glad we were able to help.
        Matthias: I don't think we could have done it without you, {$playerName}.
    -> Player: I can't believe they got away.
        Matthias: I know. 
        Matthias: But if it hadn't been for you, it would have been a lot worse.
Captain Drake: I need to speak to the crew as soon as possible. 
Captain Drake: We should be almost at Omen City Port. 
Captain Drake: Please, allow me to escort you both back upstairs.
===

