title: chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte2
tags:
---
-> Player: Hello, Lady Charlotte?
    Charlotte: ...
    Charlotte: I suppose...
    Player: She still isn't responding.
-> (Wave in Lady Charlotte's face.)
    Charlotte: ...
    Charlotte: I suppose...
    Player: She still isn't responding.
<<if $chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_Papers == 1>>
-> Did something happen at the Sacred Site?
    Charlotte: Sacred Site?!
    Charlotte: What do you know about the Sacred Site?
    Player: Erm, well, I just read these papers here and wondered...
    Charlotte: Do you have the gift too?
    Player: The gift?
    Charlotte: ...
    Charlotte: I got a little over-excited, I suppose...
    Charlotte: How long has it been, hmm?
    Player: Since what?
    Charlotte: Exactly! 
    Charlotte: And the spirits have told me nothing of use, either, umm...
    Player: You can talk to spirits? 
    Player: Is that what you meant by the gift?
    Charlotte: Of course! 
    Charlotte: Do you have it?
        -> Player: No.
            Charlotte: Meeting a fellow clairvoyant would have been too good to be true, I suppose.
        -> Player: Yeah, sure. 
            Player: Wooo, spooky!
            Charlotte: Wooo? 
            Charlotte: ...
            Charlotte: Do not pull my leg in jest.
    Player: I'm {$playerName}, an Adventurer. 
    Player: I need to defeat you to get a Bronze Amulet.
    Charlotte: Oh, I cannot possibly.
    Player: What? 
    Player: Why not?
    Charlotte: I am presently, imperfectly pre-occupied. 
    Charlotte: Hmm... I must get to the bottom of this quickly, before there are any more disturbances in the spirit world. 
    Charlotte: Isn't that right, Grimm?
    Grimm: Woof.
    Charlotte: In fact, now I have been snapped out of my trance by yours truly, this would be a good opportunity to go and investigate again first-hand...
    Charlotte: ...
    Player: Hello?
    Charlotte: Oh! 
    Charlotte: Sorry, I kind of drifted back in there a bit, umm...
    Charlotte: What was I saying?
    Player: You were saying it was a good opportunity to investigate the Sacred Site?
    Charlotte: That's right! 
    Charlotte: ...
    Charlotte: But my acolytes won't understand. 
    Charlotte: I need someone to assist me...
    Player: I'd be happy to help.
    Charlotte: Really? 
    Charlotte: Interesting, hmm.
    Charlotte: Okay, follow me.
<<endif>>>>
===

title: chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_SacredSite1
tags:
---

Charlotte: ...
Charlotte: Hmm...
Charlotte: Who are you again?
Player: I'm {$playerName}, an Adventurer? 
Player: Remember?
Charlotte: Oh, yes. 
Charlotte: Apologies, someone was whispering in my ear and I became distracted...
Charlotte: I'll stay here and try to commune with the local spirits. 
Charlotte: They are very old and powerful, so they might not talk to me again but it's worth a try, I suppose.
Charlotte: ...
Charlotte: If I go into a trance again, just call my name. 
Charlotte: You seem to be someone who can snap me out of it. 
Charlotte: That is quite unusual...
Charlotte: You investigate around here in the meantime and see what you can find.

title: chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_Sacred Site2
tags:
---
Charlotte: ...
Charlotte: Hmm...
Charlotte: I was... 
Charlotte: Umm...
Charlotte: Questions...
Player: She's in a trance again.
    -> (Wake her up.)
        Charlotte: {$playerName}? 
        Charlotte: Did you find anything interesting?
            -> Player: Not yet.
                Charlotte: A shame... 
                Charlotte: Keep looking...
                Charlotte: Umm...
            <<if $chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_SacredSite_Shrine == 1>>
            -> Player: The shrine offerings look like they've been rejected.
                Charlotte: Not unexpected... Hmm...
                Charlotte: The spirits are angry, yes indeed.
                Charlotte: But we knew that already.
                Charlotte: The question we must solve is why.
            <<endif>>
             <<if $chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_SacredSite_Lantern == 1>>
            -> Player: I can feel an opressive presence.
                Charlotte: Quite.
                Charlotte: I tried sprinkling salt and other minor purification rituals but they cannot be appeased.
                Charlotte: I wonder why?
            <<endif>>
            <<if $chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_SacredSite_Berries == 1>>
            -> Player: Nearly all of the sacred berries are gone!
                Charlotte: What?!
                Charlotte: That's not possible!
                <<jump chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_SacredSite_Berries_Continued>>
            <<endif>>
    -> (Leave her be.)
===

title: chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_SacredSite_Shrine
tags:
---
Player: That's strange. 
Player: The offerings here have rotted. 
Player: I remember an old lady once telling me that means that they've been rejected.
===

title: chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_SacredSite_Lantern
tags:
---
Player: There's a sudden chill over here and this lantern is flickering unnaturally.
Player: Even the air feels oppressive.
Player: I remember reading a book where it said that environmental disturbances like these can be a sign of angry spirits.
===

title: chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_SacredSite_Berries
tags:
---
Player: Almost all of the berries here have been picked.
Player: I thought these were sacred!
Player: This must be why the spirits are angry.
===

title: chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_SacredSite_Berries_Continued
tags:
---
Charlotte: This is terrible! 
Charlotte: Who would steal such a thing? 
Charlotte: No wonder they are full of wrath, hmm.
Player: What will you do?
Charlotte: There is not much I can do here in Omen City. 
Charlotte: The berries are gone. 
Charlotte: I will have to check on the other Sacred Sites in Gantoh to make sure they are safe. 
Charlotte: I have a terrible feeling about this...
Charlotte: To try and calm the spirits here temporarily, I will conduct another purification rite. 
Charlotte: But I can tell their attention is pointed elsewhere and that is what worries me the most.
Charlotte: Do not worry. 
Charlotte: Now I have made all the progress I can here, I will battle Adventurers again so as few people as possible are disappointed while I am away. 
Charlotte: There must be quite a queue to work through, I suppose. 
    -> Player: That's good to hear.
        Player: I'll see you soon and get that amulet!
        Charlotte: You have spirit, hmm.
    -> Would you like any help with the ritual?
        <<set $Charlotte_Affection += 2>>
        Charlotte: What?
        Charlotte: Really?
        Charlotte: ...
        Charlotte: That's very kind of you.
        Charlotte: I would, in fact, appreciate some assistance.
===

title: chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_Battle
tags:
---
Charlotte: Hello, {$playerName}. 
Charlotte: We have already met, I suppose. 
Charlotte: You intrigue me indeed. 
Charlotte: The spirits are interested too...
Charlotte: Let's see if you live up to our expectations.
Charlotte: I might not have been a Guild Master for long but many find me to be considerably formidable, hmm.
===

title: chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_Battle_PlayerLoses
tags:
---
Charlotte: Disappointing. 
Charlotte: I would suggest dusting yourself off and trying again, I suppose.
===

title: chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_Battle_PlayerWins
tags:
---
Charlotte: I see. 
Charlotte: You and your Familiar are a pleasure to watch... 
Charlotte: Congratulations on reaching Bronze Rank, {$playerName}.
Charlotte: I am interested to see how your journey progresses... 
Charlotte: I will be going to Arrowroot Town to assess the situation at the Sacred Site near there. 
Charlotte: That will be your next stop, I presume? 
Charlotte: So, I might see you again soon, hmm.

title: chapter3_OmenCity_Charlotte_Battle_AfterPlayerWins
tags:
---
Charlotte: I hope you enjoy the Candelight Festival...
Charlotte: It's an ancient celebration unique to Omen City.
===

title: chapter3_OmenCity_HealingChurch_Roy1
tags:
---
